br />\n<br />\n我之前都係果個山頭讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f44018db2284a3468a94bb5ec96b8d8a25bbc51a","tid":155142,"uid":3935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:59:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屯門 vs 小西灣 <br />\n<br />\n唔介意送佢返去 因為都幾喜歡坐巴士望住佢訓個個樣。 回程佢又會陪我講電話或者視像。<br />\n<br />\n不過過左尾班車就大獲少少，因為單程連等車最少兩個至三個鐘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同地方, 多數係我去小西搵佢到夜晚自己走, 唔會講電話唔會視訊, 都係當面見(我地係同學)/ wtsapp 多<br />\n<br />\n不過我未試過晏過11點走, 我懷疑因為佢唔想我搞到佢打唔到機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 今日未到十點就比佢趕左番屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94601017430e4939e3cde30d4b365df123795a4d","tid":155142,"uid":51924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T19:23:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上嚟訓</blockquote><br />\n正解 順手半同居"},{"pid":"25f1086c625104790531da053f0848ce7ef5861f","tid":155142,"uid":26003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T20:54:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大埔 筲箕灣<br />\n維繫唔到</blockquote><br />\n大埔好似有巴士去西彎河嗰邊？<br />\n<br />\n利申: 嚟緊搬去大埔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有都冇時間<br />\n佢話返工攰淨係星期五或星期六先見一次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBtw巴打搬去大埔邊度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要搭shuttle bus 上山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前都係果個山頭讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我廢事自爆喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 成日聽講大埔多嘢食，但我平時只係踩單車先會去大埔，有冇大埔JJ 講吓大埔有咩好食？例如早餐有冇邊間茶記好食？我母親好鐘意去茶記食早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b8ac419d70174334943df4f2bc5be12d878093","tid":155142,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime